<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249395>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 15. Stethantyx alajuela sp. nov., Ƥ: 11 — head, frontal; 14 — whole insect without wings, left. Stethantyx heredia sp. nov., Ƥ: 12 — head, frontal. Stethantyx sanjosea sp. nov., Ƥ: 13 — head, frontal. Stethantyx propodeator sp. nov., Ƥ: 15 — head, mesosoma and first metasomal segment, left." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249398>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 29. Stethantyx alajuela sp. nov., Ƥ: 24 — mesosoma, left; 25 — mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal. Stethantyx aprica sp. nov., Ƥ: 26 — head, frontal; 27 — mesosoma and first metasomal segment, left; 28 — propodeum, posterolateral. Stethantyx altamira sp. nov., Ƥ: 29 — mesosoma, left. Scale bars (except Fig. 27) = 0.1 mm, scale bar for Fig. 27 = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249398/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249402>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47 – 52. Stethantyx punarenasa sp. nov., Ƥ: 47 — mesosoma, left; 48 — mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal; 49 — propodeum, dorsal. Stethantyx sanjosea sp. nov., Ƥ: 50 — mesosoma, dorsal. Stethantyx cartagoa sp. nov., Ƥ: 51 — mesosoma, left; 52 — propodeum, dorsal. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249402/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249399>
    dc:description "FIGURES 30 – 35. Stethantyx curvator sp. nov., Ƥ: 30 — propodeum, dorsal. Stethantyx altamira sp. nov., Ƥ: 31 — ovipositor, left. Stethantyx guanacasteca sp. nov., Ƥ: 32 — mesosoma, left; 33 — propodeum, dorsal. Stethantyx heredia sp. nov., Ƥ: 34 — mesosoma, left; 35 — mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249401>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40 – 46. Stethantyx niger sp. nov., Ƥ: 40 — apex of ovipositor, left. Stethantyx orosia sp. nov., Ƥ: 41 — head, frontal; 42 — mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal; 43 — mesosoma, left; 44 — propodeum, dorsal. Stethantyx osa sp. nov., Ƥ: 45 — head, frontal. Stethantyx pseudoorosia sp. nov., Ƥ: 46 — head, frontal. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249404>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56 – 59. Stethantyx cacaoensis sp. nov., Ƥ: 56 — habitus, left (holotype). Stethantyx cartagoa sp. nov., Ƥ: 57 — antenna, left. Stethantyx mesoscutator sp. nov., 3: 58 — head and mesosoma, left; 59 — propodeum and base of metasoma, dorsolateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249404/files/figure.png" ;
