<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249405>
    dc:description "FIGURES 60 – 65. Stethantyx nigrofemorata sp. nov., Ƥ: 60 — head, frontal; 61 — head and mesosoma, left; 62 — propodeum, dorsal; 63 — metasoma and legs, left. Stethantyx tenoriosa sp. nov., Ƥ: 64 — head and mesosoma, left; 65 — propodeum and base of metasoma, dorsolateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249405/files/figure.png" ;
