<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249403>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53 – 55. Stethantyx sanjosea sp. nov., Ƥ: 53 — propodeum, dorsal; 54 — mesosoma and hind leg, left. Stethantyx limona sp. nov., Ƥ: 55 — propodeum, dorsal. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
